------------------------------------
词根(root)  duce
duce = duct = lead 引导 v-->n 意思不变

intro=inner
introduce 
introduction


reduce = re+duce
reduce-->reduction
-------------------------------------



ag,act 
	 to do /to drive   起源于拉丁动词agere,表示to do (做)或者 to drive(驱使)
agency  [ag+ency] -ency 性质或状态|办事的场所能力
	 //a business or an organization that provides a particular service especially on behalf of other business or organizations

--eg:international aid agencies caring for refugees  国际援助难民事务所



agenda  [ag+enda]   --end 抽象名词后缀  -a表示复数
    // a list of items to be discussed or to be done

--eg:For the government,education is now at the top of the agenda. 对政府来说,教育是当务之急.


agile  -ile=able 能...的;有..能力的
	// able to move quickly and easily [敏捷的]| able to think quickly and in an intelligent way [机灵的]

--eg: an agile mind 敏捷的思维  syn:nimble 


action [act+ion] --ion = the process or result 表示过程或结果
	// process of doing,or deed 行动  --eg: Action speaks louder than words
	//result of doing sth,or effect 作用  --eg:the action of an acid on mental 
	//charge [诉讼] --eg:to bring an action against sb 起诉某人

